This commissioned artwork captures a lighthearted yet gentle scene between two characters standing together in their school uniforms. One figure carries a playful presence with bunny ears and a relaxed stance, while the other stands with composed confidence, exuding calm charm. Since this is a commissioned piece, it means a lot to me to hear how it makes others feel too. Does it make you smile, or maybe remind you of a friendship of your own? I would love to hear your thoughts.
